# CQ-017: Which platforms have the most energy news posts?
PREFIX enews: <http://example.org/ontology/energy-news#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT ?platform ?platformLabel (COUNT(?post) AS ?postCount) WHERE {
    ?post a enews:Post ;
          enews:postedBy ?author .
    ?author enews:onPlatform ?platform .
    ?platform rdfs:label ?platformLabel .
}
GROUP BY ?platform ?platformLabel
ORDER BY DESC(?postCount)
